    21	
    22	Three limit concepts are deliberately distinct and must not be conflated:
    23	
    24	- **Acceptance profile** (baseline §Acceptance profiles): system-level trial statistics
    25	  (for example ≤ 25 m aided, ≤ 200 m denied horizontal position) computed offline over
