    27	  states they **do not replace per-epoch integrity and authority checks**.
    28	- **Protection limit**: the per-epoch bound the authority supervisor tests each solution
    29	  against, derived by the solution integrity monitor (architecture module 10) from the
    30	  filter covariance and integrity state, *independently of ArduPilot*. The baseline does not
    31	  supply protection-limit numbers; they are **[UNVERIFIED]** and shall be no looser than the
    32	  active acceptance profile implies.
